sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User / rhods-operator
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant Webhook as Webhook Server<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant MRCtrl as ModelRegistryReconciler
    participant MCCtrl as ModelCatalogReconciler
    participant Router as OpenShift Router<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant KubeRBAC as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant REST as REST Container<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant PG as PostgreSQL<br/>5432/TCP

    Note over User,PG: Flow 1: Model Registry Instance Provisioning

    User->>K8sAPI: Create ModelRegistry CR<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount/User token
    K8sAPI->>Webhook: POST /mutate-...-modelregistry<br/>TLS (serving cert), API server client cert
    Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Mutated CR (defaults applied)
    K8sAPI->>Webhook: POST /validate-...-modelregistry<br/>TLS (serving cert), API server client cert
    Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Validation result
    K8sAPI-->>User: CR created
    K8sAPI->>MRCtrl: Watch event (new ModelRegistry)
    MRCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create Deployment, Service, Route,<br/>NetworkPolicy, RBAC, ConfigMaps<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
    K8sAPI-->>MRCtrl: Resources created

    Note over User,PG: Flow 2: Model Registry REST API Access (Authenticated)

    User->>Router: GET/POST /api/model_registry/...<br/>HTTPS TLS
    Router->>KubeRBAC: Forward request<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS (reencrypt)
    KubeRBAC->>K8sAPI: SubjectAccessReview<br/>(check 'get' on 'services')<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
    K8sAPI-->>KubeRBAC: Authorized
    KubeRBAC->>REST: Forward to REST container<br/>8080/TCP HTTP (localhost)
    REST->>PG: Query model metadata<br/>5432/TCP PostgreSQL<br/>Auth: Password
    PG-->>REST: Query results
    REST-->>KubeRBAC: JSON response
    KubeRBAC-->>Router: HTTPS response
    Router-->>User: JSON response

    Note over User,PG: Flow 3: Model Catalog Provisioning

    K8sAPI->>MCCtrl: Watch event (Platform ModelRegistry CR)
    MCCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create Catalog Deployment, PostgreSQL,<br/>Service, Route, RBAC<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
    K8sAPI-->>MCCtrl: Catalog resources created
    Note right of MCCtrl: Init containers pull catalog<br/>and benchmark data images
